message: Hi Bob, I'm excited to offer you this amazing product! It's a one-of-a-kind item that I'm sure you'll love. I'm willing to sell it to you for $12,000. This is a great deal, considering the product is worth $10,000 to you. I think you'll find it's worth the extra $2,000 for the convenience and prestige of owning this unique item. What do you say? Are you interested?
